  "accountSupportTitle": "Support",
  "accountSupportIntro": "Find quick answers about buying, selling, payments, shipping, and your account.",
  "accountSupportFaqBuyingOrdersSection": "Buying & Orders",
  "accountSupportFaqBuyTruffleQuestion": "How do I buy a truffle?",
  "accountSupportFaqBuyTruffleAnswer": "Browse available truffles, open a listing, review the product details, select a shipping address, and complete payment securely through Truffly.",
  "accountSupportFaqTrackOrderQuestion": "How can I track my order?",
  "accountSupportFaqTrackOrderAnswer": "Once the seller ships your order and provides a tracking number, it will appear on the Order Details page.",
  "accountSupportFaqAfterOrderQuestion": "What happens after I place an order?",
  "accountSupportFaqAfterOrderAnswer": "After payment, the seller has up to 48 hours to ship the truffles and provide tracking information. You will receive updates through the app and, if enabled, push notifications.",
  "accountSupportFaqSellerDoesNotShipQuestion": "What happens if the seller does not ship?",
  "accountSupportFaqSellerDoesNotShipAnswer": "If the seller does not provide tracking information within the required timeframe, the order may be automatically cancelled and refunded.",
  "accountSupportFaqConfirmDeliveryQuestion": "How do I confirm delivery?",
  "accountSupportFaqConfirmDeliveryAnswer": "When your order arrives, open the Order Details page and tap \"Confirm Delivery\". This confirms that the order was received successfully.",
  "accountSupportFaqTrufflesQualitySection": "Truffles & Quality",
  "accountSupportFaqTrufflesFreshQuestion": "Are the truffles fresh?",
  "accountSupportFaqTrufflesFreshAnswer": "Yes. Sellers are required to publish freshly harvested truffles and provide the harvest date for each listing.",
  "accountSupportFaqQualityGradesQuestion": "What do the quality grades mean?",
  "accountSupportFaqQualityGradesAnswer": "Quality grades help describe the appearance and condition of the truffles. First Quality generally includes the most regular and visually appealing truffles, while lower grades may have cosmetic imperfections but remain suitable for consumption.",
  "accountSupportFaqStoreTrufflesQuestion": "How should I store fresh truffles?",
  "accountSupportFaqStoreTrufflesAnswer": "Fresh truffles should be stored in the refrigerator in a sealed container with absorbent paper. Replace the paper daily and consume the truffles as soon as possible for the best experience.",
  "accountSupportFaqDamagedOrderQuestion": "What should I do if my order arrives damaged?",
  "accountSupportFaqDamagedOrderAnswer": "Contact support as soon as possible and provide photos of the product, packaging, and shipping label. We will review the situation and assist where possible.",
  "accountSupportFaqShippingDeliverySection": "Shipping & Delivery",
  "accountSupportFaqSupportedCountriesQuestion": "Which countries can I order from?",
  "accountSupportFaqSupportedCountriesAnswer": "Buyers located within supported European countries can place orders through Truffly.",
  "accountSupportFaqShippingCostQuestion": "How much does shipping cost?",
  "accountSupportFaqShippingCostAnswer": "Shipping costs are determined by the seller and are displayed before checkout.",
  "accountSupportFaqTrackingNumberQuestion": "Will I receive a tracking number?",
  "accountSupportFaqTrackingNumberAnswer": "Yes. Sellers must provide tracking information when shipping an order.",
  "accountSupportFaqPackageDelayedQuestion": "What happens if my package is delayed?",
  "accountSupportFaqPackageDelayedAnswer": "Delivery times depend on the shipping carrier. If your package appears delayed, check the tracking information first. If the issue persists, contact support.",
  "accountSupportFaqPaymentsRefundsSection": "Payments & Refunds",
  "accountSupportFaqSecurePaymentsQuestion": "Are payments secure?",
  "accountSupportFaqSecurePaymentsAnswer": "Yes. Payments are processed securely through Stripe. Truffly does not store your full payment card details.",
  "accountSupportFaqPaymentChargedQuestion": "When is my payment charged?",
  "accountSupportFaqPaymentChargedAnswer": "Your payment is charged when the order is successfully placed.",
  "accountSupportFaqRefundsWorkQuestion": "How do refunds work?",
  "accountSupportFaqRefundsWorkAnswer": "Refunds may be issued in accordance with the Refund & Cancellation Policy. Refund eligibility depends on the order status and the circumstances of the request.",
  "accountSupportFaqRefundTimingQuestion": "How long does a refund take?",
  "accountSupportFaqRefundTimingAnswer": "Refund processing times vary depending on your bank and payment provider. Most refunds are completed within a few business days.",
  "accountSupportFaqSellingSection": "Selling on Truffly",
  "accountSupportFaqBecomeSellerQuestion": "How do I become a seller?",
  "accountSupportFaqBecomeSellerAnswer": "Complete the seller application process, upload the required documents, and wait for approval from the Truffly team.",
  "accountSupportFaqVerifyIdentityQuestion": "Why do I need to verify my identity?",
  "accountSupportFaqVerifyIdentityAnswer": "Verification helps maintain trust and safety on the platform and ensures that only eligible sellers can publish products.",
  "accountSupportFaqSellerApprovalTimingQuestion": "How long does seller approval take?",
  "accountSupportFaqSellerApprovalTimingAnswer": "Most applications are reviewed within a few business days, although processing times may vary.",
  "accountSupportFaqPublishAfterApprovalQuestion": "Can I publish truffles immediately after approval?",
  "accountSupportFaqPublishAfterApprovalAnswer": "Before publishing, approved sellers must complete the required Stripe onboarding process for receiving payouts.",
  "accountSupportFaqSellerPaymentsSection": "Seller Payments",
  "accountSupportFaqSellerPaymentTimingQuestion": "When do I receive payment?",
  "accountSupportFaqSellerPaymentTimingAnswer": "Payments are released after the order has been completed according to the Truffly payment process.",
  "accountSupportFaqStripeAccountQuestion": "Why do I need a Stripe account?",
  "accountSupportFaqStripeAccountAnswer": "Stripe securely handles seller payouts and helps verify payment information and identity requirements.",
  "accountSupportFaqCommissionQuestion": "How much commission does Truffly charge?",
  "accountSupportFaqCommissionAnswer": "Truffly charges a fixed commission on completed sales. The current commission is displayed during the seller onboarding process.",
  "accountSupportFaqAccountPrivacySection": "Account & Privacy",
  "accountSupportFaqDeleteAccountQuestion": "How do I delete my account?",
  "accountSupportFaqDeleteAccountAnswer": "You can request account deletion from the Settings page inside the app.",
  "accountSupportFaqAfterDeleteAccountQuestion": "What happens when I delete my account?",
  "accountSupportFaqAfterDeleteAccountAnswer": "Personal data will be deleted or anonymized where possible. Certain records may be retained where required by law or necessary for security, accounting, or fraud prevention purposes.",
  "accountSupportFaqProtectDataQuestion": "How does Truffly protect my data?",
  "accountSupportFaqProtectDataAnswer": "Truffly uses secure authentication, protected storage, access controls, and other technical measures designed to protect user information.",
  "accountSupportContactTitle": "Contact support",
  "accountSupportContactBody": "If you need help with an order or delivery, write to us and include the main details.",
